      changes).
    </li>
    <li>To send release updates and announcements — only if you have explicitly opted in.</li>
    <li>To comply with legal obligations.</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Cookies and tracking</h3>
  <p>
    We use only essential first-party cookies required for authentication and session management. We
